title: The Best of The Gipsy Kings - Greatest Hits 5CD (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Here is some truly great stuff in music from the South American landscape
I'm sure.

My sister Rosie and my brother-in-law Jose (a greatest of men - and from
Chile as it turns out) introduced me to this great music and I have a few favourite
songs that are done by them including "Escucha me" - when we tested this song
here comparing FLAC to mp3, there was no doubt the mp3 sounded fuller and
had much more impact in the sound effect it produced in this case.

So here are all five "Original Series" CDs from the 2013 issue which contain
all I can think of in regards to their Greatest hits or Best musical numbers.

Please seed this fine music to the ears

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
